    org.apache.juneau.transforms
    Predefined Transform implementations

    • Uses of DateSwap in org.apache.juneau.transforms

      Subclasses of DateSwap in org.apache.juneau.transforms 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  DateSwap.ISO8601DT
      Transforms Dates to ISO8601 date-time strings.
      static class  DateSwap.ISO8601DTP
      Same as DateSwap.ISO8601DT except serializes to millisecond precision.
      static class  DateSwap.ISO8601DTPNZ
      Same as DateSwap.ISO8601DT except serializes to millisecond precision and doesn't include timezone.
      static class  DateSwap.ISO8601DTZ
      Same as DateSwap.ISO8601DT, except always serializes in GMT.
      static class  DateSwap.ISO8601DTZP
      Same as DateSwap.ISO8601DTZ except serializes to millisecond precision.
      static class  DateSwap.Medium
      Transforms Dates to DateFormat.MEDIUM strings.
      static class  DateSwap.RFC2822D
      Transforms Dates to RFC2822 date strings.
      static class  DateSwap.RFC2822DT
      Transforms Dates to RFC2822 date-time strings.
      static class  DateSwap.RFC2822DTZ
      Same as DateSwap.RFC2822DT, except always serializes in GMT.
      static class  DateSwap.SimpleDT
      Transforms Dates to simple "yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm:ss" strings.
      static class  DateSwap.SimpleDTP
      Transforms Dates to simple "yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm:ss.SSS" strings.
      static class  DateSwap.SimpleT
      Transforms Dates to simple "HH:mm:ss" strings.
      static class  DateSwap.SimpleTP
      Transforms Dates to simple "HH:mm:ss.SSS" strings.
      static class  DateSwap.ToString
      Transforms Dates to Strings using the Date.toString() method.
